Although not meant to be comprehensive, here is a list of
suggested actions for employers to take to improve their work
place. These suggestions resulted from noting some of the
most frequently cited sections or for which particularly large
fines were assessed.
1. Post posters (in appropriate language) informing em-
ployees of the obligations and protection provided by
the law. The poster may not be altered, defaced or cov-
